      "description": "We are proud to present this masterfully preserved specimen, a vehicle that transcends the standard used market. Maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains in a state of absolute refinement, showing no signs of wear. This vehicle has been subjected to a rigorous technical evaluation, confirming that its performance and mechanical integrity are indistinguishable from its original production state. For the sophisticated buyer seeking an uncompromising automotive investment, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless example.",
      "price": 48900.0,
