    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super careful with it, and it shows in every little detail. It\u2019s spotlessly clean, runs like a total dream, and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
