    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six with factory-spec individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally flawless, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already addressed. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. Every bushing is tight, the Bilstein PSS10 dampers provide exceptional turn-in response, and the rod bearings have been serviced preventatively. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint correction needed, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather bolsters and an untouched dashboard. This is a concours-level driver\u2019s machine for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
